      • getLast

        public static <V> V getLast(V[] sourceArray,
                            V value,
                            V defaultValue,
                            boolean isCircle)
        找到数组中最后一个满足对比条件的变量 get last element of the target element, before the first one that match the target element front to back
        • if array is empty, return defaultValue
        • if target element is not exist in array, return defaultValue
        • if target element exist in array and its index is not 0, return the last element
        • if target element exist in array and its index is 0, return the last one in array if isCircle is true, else return defaultValue
        类型参数:
        V -
        参数:
        sourceArray -
        value - value of target element
        defaultValue - default return value
        isCircle - whether is circle
        返回:

      • getNext

        public static <V> V getNext(V[] sourceArray,
                            V value,
                            V defaultValue,
                            boolean isCircle)
        获取下一个满足条件的元素 get next element of the target element, after the first one that match the target element front to back
        • if array is empty, return defaultValue
        • if target element is not exist in array, return defaultValue
        • if target element exist in array and not the last one in array, return the next element
        • if target element exist in array and the last one in array, return the first one in array if isCircle is true, else return defaultValue
        类型参数:
        V -
        参数:
        sourceArray -
        value - value of target element
        defaultValue - default return value
        isCircle - whether is circle
        返回:
